The paper presents a novel application of LSTM recurrent neural networks to multilabel classification of diagnoses given variable-length time series of clinical measurements. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV).
